- happy path
- onboarding
- authentication
- persistence
- navigation
- synchronization

## Error Flows
- network failures
- timeout handling
- retries
- invalid payloads
- session expiration
- SDK failures

## Edge Cases
- duplicate actions
- rapid interactions
- offline transitions
- empty states
- invalid state recovery
- interrupted flows

